subject: Soccer
lead_paragraph: Defending champion Manchester United cruised to a 3-0 victory at second-tier Southampton in the F.A. Cup and will host Tottenham in the fourth round. Two goals by James Milner gave Aston Villa a 2-1 victory at Gillingham of League One.
